name: Cute Cartoon Illustration
description:
This is just a merge of toonify legacy and Samaritan 3d Cartoon and my other lora. Very good making different facial expression and forest jungle scene looks beautiful

I Use hires. fix, upscale latent, denoising 0.5, hires steps 20, upscale by 2 . Clip skip 2 .

I use night sky yozora VAE in the examples https://civitai.com/api/download/models/14459?type=VAE

if you like the models, please consider supporting me on, i will continue to upload more cool stuffs in the future


patreon.com/PromptSharingSamaritan

https://ko-fi.com/promptsharingsamaritan

IF YOU'RE NEW HERE

U need to use a proper VAE or the color become pale and washed out, and it will look way better if you use hi-res fix

copy the yozora VAE to stable-diffusion-webui-master\models\VAE and then go to automatic1111 webui , click on settings tab, the go to stable diffusion tab to the left, then go to SD VAE to select which VAE u want and then click apply settings.
